NG0278:1: khro bo chen po dbyug pa sngon po dang */
NG0278:3: sprul pa'i phra men ma g.yag gi mgo can dang */
NG0278:4: bya rog gi mgo can no //
NG0278:5: om badzra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka hu~m / pa tsa pa tsa hu~m phat /
NG0278:6: khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po dang */
NG0278:7: yum dur khrod kyi bdag mo /
NG0278:8: sprul pa'i phran men ma sha ba'i mgo can dang */
NG0278:10: om badzra kro d+ha ar+ya a tsa la hu~m /
NG0278:12: khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon po dang */
NG0278:13: yum rdo rje gtun khung ma /
NG0278:14: sprul pa'i phra men ma gzig gi mgo can dang */
NG0278:16: om badzra kro d+ha ha ya gri ba hu~m /
NG0278:17: hu lu hu lu hu~m phat /
NG0278:18: khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang */
NG0278:20: sprul pa'i phra men ma byi la'i mgo can dang */
NG0278:21: pu shud kyi mgo can no //
NG0278:22: om badzra kro d+ha a pa ra dzi ta hu~m /
NG0278:24: khro bo chen po dpal ldan gzhan gyis mi thub pa dang */
NG0278:25: yum rdo rje mda' snyems ma /
NG0278:26: sprul pa'i phra men ma spyang ki'i mgo can dang */
NG0278:28: om badzra kro d+ha a mr-i ta kun+da li hu~m /
NG0278:30: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang */
NG0278:32: sprul pa'i phra men ma seng ge'i mgo can dang */
NG0278:33: pha wang gi mgo can no //
NG0278:34: om badzra kro d+ha trai lo kya bi dza ya hu~m /
NG0278:36: khro bo chen po khams sum rnam par rgyal ba dang */
NG0278:37: yum rdo rje gsod byed ma /
NG0278:38: sprul pa'i phra men ma dred kyi mgo can dang */
NG0278:40: om badzra kro d+ha ma ha ba la hu~m /  s+pho ta s+pho ta hu~m phat /
NG0278:41: khro bo chen po stobs po che dang */
NG0278:42: yum rdo rje bskyod byed ma /
NG0278:43: sprul pa'i phra men ma dred kyi mgo can dang */
NG0278:44: byi ba'i mgo can la sogs pa rnams kyis gtams pa'o //
NG0278:45: srid pa'i phur bu bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0278:46: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NG0278:47: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NG0278:48: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang *//
NG0278:49: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang *//
NG0278:50: ki la ya yi dngos grub gsol //
NG0278:51: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NG0278:52: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NG0278:53: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NG0278:54: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NG0278:55: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NG0278:56: khyed kyi phrin las dus la bab //
NG0278:57: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0278:58: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NG0278:59: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing *//
NG0278:60: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa //
NG0278:61: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NG0278:62: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NG0278:63: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NG0278:64: khro bo chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NG0278:65: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir bkug nas //
NG0278:66: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang *//
NG0278:67: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang *//
NG0278:68: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NG0278:71: mo ha ga ya b+ha ga ban /
NG0278:73: shri badzra hu~m ka ra hu~m hu~m phat phat /
NG0278:74: badzra ki li ki li ya /
NG0278:78: li ki la ya hu~m hu~m phat phat /
NG0278:79: badzra hu~m ka ra hu~m phat /
NG0278:81: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NG0278:82: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NG0278:83: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NG0278:84: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NG0278:85: rengs par khug la smrar chug cig / phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NG0278:86: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang *//
NG0278:87: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis //
NG0278:88: hu~m pa ra bi d+h+wa na hu~m phat /
NG0278:92: ha na ha na hu~m phat /
NG0278:94: ta tha ya ta tha ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:96: ra na ha ta na hu~m phat /
NG0278:97: shi krin a na ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:98: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:99: a be sha ya a be sha ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:100: bid+d+ha ya bid+d+ha ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:101: bran dang pho nya bka' nyan tshogs //
NG0278:102: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NG0278:103: sngon chad ji bzhin dam bcas pa'i //
NG0278:104: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NG0278:113: dza ye bi dza ye ya /
NG0278:114: a dzi te a pa ra dzi ta ya /
NG0278:115: ma ra sai n+yi pra marda na ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:116: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NG0278:117: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NG0278:118: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NG0278:119: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NG0278:120: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NG0278:121: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NG0278:122: hu~m ma ma pa shi ku ru /
NG0278:126: ma ma karma shri krang ka ra ya /
NG0278:127: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa yi //
NG0278:129: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NG0278:130: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NG0278:131: sarba a na ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:132: ta tha ya ta tha ya hu~m phat /
NG0278:133: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NG0278:134: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NG0278:135: rdo rje me dbal snying sregs nas //
NG0278:136: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NG0278:137: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NG0278:138: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NG0278:139: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar bya /
NG0278:144: badzra yak+sha kro d+ha kha hi /
NG0278:152: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis brlabs so //
NG0278:154: a b+hi tsar+ya'i dus la bab pa'i brnag pa de kho na la'o //
NG0278:155: ki li ki la ya nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas //
